"title": "8160: seeking God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8160: seeking god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's desire is that all people should seek after him and find him. Those who seek God with all their heart are rewarded, but those who fail to seek him do so to their eternal loss.</p>\n<h2>God's heart is for people to seek him</h2>\n<h3>God wants people to seek him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:27\">ACT 17:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:11\">1CH 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:19\">1CH 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:2\">PSA 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:16-Acts15:17\">ACT 15:16–15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:11-Amos9:12\">AMO 9:11–9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></p>\n<h3>God calls people to seek him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6-Isa55:7\">ISA 55:6–55:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:12\">HOS 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:4-Amos5:6\">AMO 5:4–5:6</a></p>\n<h3>God promises that people will seek him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:4\">JER 50:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:4-Hos3:5\">HOS 3:4–3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:13-Hos5:15\">HOS 5:13–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:3\">ZEP 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:20-Zech8:23\">ZEC 8:20–8:23</a></p>\n<h3>God promises to be found by those who seek him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:17\">PRO 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:29-Deut4:31\">DEU 4:29–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:1-2Chr15:2\">2CH 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:19\">ISA 45:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11-Jer29:14\">JER 29:11–29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:8\">MAT 7:7–7:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:10\">LUK 11:9–11:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's opportunity for seeking him is now and is restricted to this life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:31\">LUK 16:19–16:31</a></p>\n<h2>Seeking God is an issue of the heart</h2>\n<h3>Seeking God begins in the heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:8\">PSA 27:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:16\">2CH 11:16</a></p>\n<h3>Wholeheartedness in seeking God is required</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:13\">JER 29:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:27-Deut4:29\">DEU 4:27–4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:17-1Chr22:19\">1CH 22:17–22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:12-2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:12–15:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a></p>\n<h2>Seeking God and his kingdom is the priority of life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:31\">LUK 12:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:44–13:46</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people seeking God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:11-2Kgs22:20\">2KI 22:11–22:20</a> <em>Josiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:2-2Chr14:7\">2CH 14:2–14:7</a> <em>Asa</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:3-2Chr17:6\">2CH 17:3–17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:1-2Chr20:4\">2CH 20:1–20:4</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21-Ezra8:23\">EZR 8:21–8:23</a> <em>Ezra</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4-Ps27:8\">PSA 27:4–27:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:2-Dan9:3\">DAN 9:2–9:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:1–13:3</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of seeking God</h2>\n<h3>It leads to life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:4-Amos5:6\">AMO 5:4–5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:32\">PSA 69:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7-Rom2:8\">ROM 2:7–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:18-2Chr30:20\">2CH 30:18–30:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6-Isa55:7\">ISA 55:6–55:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:17-Jer26:19\">JER 26:17–26:19</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:2\">PSA 119:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:6\">PSA 24:3–24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:9-Isa65:10\">ISA 65:9–65:10</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to provision</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:8-Ps34:10\">PSA 34:8–34:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:31–6:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:29–12:31</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to protection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4-Ps27:5\">PSA 27:4–27:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21-Ezra8:23\">EZR 8:21–8:23</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to understanding and wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:5\">PRO 28:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:17-Dan2:23\">DAN 2:17–2:23</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to renewed strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:30-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:30–40:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42-Luke22:43\">LUK 22:42–22:43</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to rejoicing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:10\">1CH 16:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:16\">PSA 40:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps70:4\">PSA 70:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:3\">PSA 105:3</a></p>\n<h2>Hindrances to seeking God</h2>\n<h3>Unrighteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:12-Hos10:13\">HOS 10:12–10:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a></p>\n<h3>Pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4\">PSA 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16-2Chr26:18\">2CH 26:16–26:18</a></p>\n<h3>Trusting in human resources</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1\">ISA 31:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:12\">2CH 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:13-Hos5:15\">HOS 5:13–5:15</a></p>\n<h3>Idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:4-Zeph1:6\">ZEP 1:4–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:21–1:23</a></p>\n<h3>Superficial religion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:5-Amos5:6\">AMO 5:5–5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:1-Isa58:9\">ISA 58:1–58:9</a></p>\n<h2>Seeking God through occult practices is forbidden</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13-1Chr10:14\">1CH 10:13–10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:31\">LEV 19:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:6\">LEV 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:10-Deut18:12\">DEU 18:10–18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:4-1Sam28:20\">1SA 28:4–28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:16-Acts16:18\">ACT 16:16–16:18</a></p>\n<h2>Consequences of not seeking God</h2>\n<h3>Loss of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:13\">2CH 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:6-Deut13:10\">DEU 13:6–13:10</a></p>\n<h3>Loss of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:155\">PSA 119:155</a></strong></p>",
